1
00:00:33,670 --> 00:00:36,280
[Mei Dong, Wanted Criminal]

2
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:35,770
Mr. Zhou.

3
00:00:37,030 --> 00:00:37,520
Dong,

4
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,200
how have you been?

5
00:00:39,790 --> 00:00:41,070
Things are good,

6
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,200
all thanks to you.

7
00:00:42,330 --> 00:00:44,200
Is there something you need, Rong?

8
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,230
Come on.

9
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,110
As your buddy,

10
00:00:46,110 --> 00:00:47,710
I just called to check on you.

11
00:00:47,750 --> 00:00:49,410
Can't I show some care for you?

12
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,580
Of course, you can.

13
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,280
My Rong always looks out for his men.

14
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,490
Alright, cut the nonsense.

15
00:00:56,110 --> 00:00:57,170
There's something

16
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,430
I need your help with.

17
00:00:58,430 --> 00:00:59,520
Just say it, Rong.

18
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:01,030
No matter what it is,

19
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:02,610
I'll get it done for you.

20
00:01:03,390 --> 00:01:04,140
I've got

21
00:01:04,230 --> 00:01:05,950
300 million sitting idle right now.

22
00:01:05,950 --> 00:01:06,950
Help me transfer it from the country

23
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:07,880
to your account.

24
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,560
Rong, give me a second.

25
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:10,950
I...

26
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:12,070
Let go of me.

27
00:01:13,510 --> 00:01:14,039
Let's go.

28
00:01:20,510 --> 00:01:20,950
Rong,

29
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:23,430
h-how much?

30
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:25,080
300 million.

31
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,000
Is it urgent?

32
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,450
The sooner, the better.

33
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,710
Rong,

34
00:01:34,950 --> 00:01:36,310
with an amount this big

35
00:01:37,070 --> 00:01:38,600
and you being in such a rush,

36
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:41,820
the handling fee

37
00:01:42,150 --> 00:01:43,350
is gonna be a bit high.

38
00:01:44,110 --> 00:01:44,850
How much?

39
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:48,560
Thirty percent.

40
00:01:48,789 --> 00:01:50,650
You're that desperate for money?

41
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,640
Rong,

42
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,620
if we're not in a hurry,

43
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,150
I can transfer it
in small batches over time.

44
00:01:58,150 --> 00:02:00,480
I guarantee I can get it done
in half a year.

45
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,610
I charge everyone else 15%,

46
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,890
but for you, I'll do 10%.

47
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,860
How's that?

48
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,800
I'm okay with 10%.

49
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,470
What about the half-year timeframe?

50
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:11,730
Half a year is too long.

51
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,370
I've got palms to grease

52
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,630
at every level.

53
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,750
I can't help it either.

54
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:19,910
Dong,

55
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,560
you think I, Zhou Rong,

56
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:24,090
can't find anyone else
to launder money, huh?

57
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,510
Rong,

58
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,560
the scrutiny on domestic accounts

59
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,030
right now is insane.

60
00:02:30,460 --> 00:02:31,850
If you don't trust me,

61
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,910
you can ask around.

62
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,490
But I guarantee

63
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,250
nobody launders money

64
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,829
faster or safer

65
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:41,490
[Faster, Safer]

66
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,079
than me.

67
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:09,190
[Born with Luck]

68
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:12,170
[Episode 13]

69
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:30,750
Chief.

70
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,310
Chief!

71
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,500
Still nothing

72
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,460
from Zhou Rong and Lang Bowen?

73
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,420
Chief,

74
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:50,790
how about this?

75
00:04:54,570 --> 00:04:56,630
We can't just keep waiting like this.

76
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,270
We need to do something.

77
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:07,720
Chief!

78
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,980
I've got a clue.

79
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:17,750
This is

80
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:19,720
the surveillance footage of the kidnappers
that we found

81
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,790
based on the clues
provided by Zheng Yongbing.

82
00:05:21,790 --> 00:05:24,310
[Hexiang Road]

83
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:25,750
It's these two.

84
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,880
Can't see their faces clearly though.

85
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:32,690
[Hexiang Road]

86
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,000
You can't see their faces,

87
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,600
so how do you know

88
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,430
it's these two?

89
00:05:34,430 --> 00:05:35,480
Why are we back on

90
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:37,040
the provincial capital case again?

91
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,380
Chief Zhang, I think...

92
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,659
Take a look at this.

93
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:44,260
[Sanjiangkou South Toll Gate]

94
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,670
This is the footage

95
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,510
from the highway entrance

96
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,920
30 meters away, two minutes later.

97
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,720
What's wrong?

98
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,750
Why didn't these two suspects

99
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:48,870
appear again

100
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:49,800
on the roadside?

101
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,720
[Sanjiangkou South]

102
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,080
They got into a vehicle.

103
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,430
That's their car.

104
00:05:59,310 --> 00:06:01,040
PingC·08915.

105
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,120
Find this vehicle.

106
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:02,480
Yes.

107
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,480
Wait a minute!

108
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:06,870
Chief Zhang,

109
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:08,240
I've reported it
to the Provincial Department.

110
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:08,950
The Criminal Investigation Corps
has ordered us

111
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,360
to cooperate fully with
the provincial task force.

112
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,600
They'll be here tomorrow.

113
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,750
If they have any requests,

114
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,350
we'll fully cooperate then.

115
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,040
Right now, our full focus

116
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,430
is to find these two people.

117
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:18,030
Find them.

118
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:21,480
What about

119
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,510
our own case then?

120
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,940
Borne on a favorable wind,

121
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,380
I'll rise to the clouds.

122
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:43,260
[Taxi]

123
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,370
Look!

124
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,640
I told you there was!

125
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:45,970
What is that?

126
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:48,220
It's so heavy.

127
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,720
This is so cool.

128
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,580
With this...

129
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,810
The crowning touch, see?

130
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:55,780
[Taxi]

131
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,900
[Taxi]

132
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:06,580
What the heck are you doing?
You scared me.

133
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:16,030
Now we can take passengers.

134
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,570
Dropping our own case to go play assistant

135
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:30,000
for someone else?

136
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,790
I'm going to see Chief Zhang.

137
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:34,700
Captain Wang!

138
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,880
Captain Wang.

139
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:36,640
Speak.

140
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,159
Do you know who's in charge of
the provincial capital explosion case?

141
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:40,590
Who?

142
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,400
Yan Liang.

143
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,830
Captain of
the Provincial Criminal Investigation Corps.

144
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:44,630
I don't care who he is!

145
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:45,870
We should handle our own cases!

146
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:46,720
Captain Wang,

147
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:49,480
how do you still not understand
the Chief's intentions?

148
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,240
Yan Liang

149
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:53,310
is a well-known criminal psychology expert
in the province.

150
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,800
He once deduced a suspect's escape plan

151
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,860
from nothing but their handwriting.

152
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,320
He's a legendary figure.

153
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,860
Think about it—

154
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,320
if we cooperate with him this time,

155
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,480
it's only reasonable

156
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,720
that he supports us with something, right?

157
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,360
No matter how cunning
Zhou Rong and Lang Bowen are,

158
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,960
can they really be his match?

159
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,680
Yan Liang and his team
will arrive tomorrow.

160
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,140
All the more reason not to!

161
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,190
Come on, everyone!

162
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,790
Drop whatever you're doing!

163
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,730
Chief Zhang,

164
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,820
look.

165
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,390
Not just the criminal investigation unit,

166
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,390
but everyone in the station

167
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:30,730
who's free

168
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,289
has been pulled in to help.

169
00:08:32,390 --> 00:08:33,850
At this rate of screening,

170
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,200
that Xiali car—

171
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,120
I'll tell you straight—

172
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,120
won't escape even if it grows wings!

173
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,570
Is this really appropriate?

174
00:08:39,570 --> 00:08:40,480
Will it hold everyone up...

175
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,210
As long as we can solve the case.

176
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,440
Chief,

177
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,370
found it.

178
00:08:47,330 --> 00:08:49,550
This was captured
on the early morning of the 3rd.

179
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:52,000
[Ping'an West Road, Sanjiangkou,
Ping'an Province]

180
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,050
Okay.

181
00:09:00,070 --> 00:09:01,390
Find these two cars!

182
00:09:20,730 --> 00:09:21,830
[Zhou Rong]

183
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,030
Hello, who is it?

184
00:09:28,510 --> 00:09:29,260
It's me.

185
00:09:29,730 --> 00:09:30,450
Mr. Zhou.

186
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:31,720
Anything up?

187
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,450
Alright, do it your way.

188
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:35,080
So what's the next step?

189
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,770
Mr. Zhou, next,

190
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:38,980
we can do this.

191
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,960
I'll find a safe place,

192
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:42,270
register a company,

193
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,840
and then hire a lawyer

194
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,900
to contact your company officially.

195
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,290
The last image of that car

196
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:51,630
was captured on this road.

197
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:53,480
But the suburban cameras are sparse,

198
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,940
so it's hard to pinpoint
its exact location.

199
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:01,090
Buddy, need a cab?

200
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:01,720
Need a cab?

201
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:02,320
No.

202
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:03,890
We just started our business.

203
00:10:03,890 --> 00:10:05,320
Yeah, we can give you a discount.

204
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,720
Not even with a discount.

205
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:07,910
Hold on.

206
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,710
Where are you going?

207
00:10:16,540 --> 00:10:17,520
Nowhere. Go.

208
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:21,990
-Nut. Seriously.
-What does that mean?

209
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,060
This guy...

210
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,400
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

211
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:43,960
Song Xing is still looking for the car,

212
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,420
but there isn't much hope.

213
00:10:47,310 --> 00:10:49,360
Yan Liang and his team are almost here.

214
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,890
We've found the Land Rover!

215
00:10:51,570 --> 00:10:52,100
Found it?

216
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,690
Yes.

217
00:10:56,940 --> 00:10:57,870
How many kidnappers are in the car?

218
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:58,770
Both of them.

219
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,650
Where are they now?

220
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:01,450
Senbo Expressway Toll Station.

221
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,790
That means they've left Sanjiangkou.

222
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:04,050
They've left the city.

223
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,660
Chase them immediately.

224
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:06,750
Tell the canteen to prepare lunch!

225
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:07,840
Yan Liang and the others are almost here!

226
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,320
We have to give the Provincial Department
a big gift!

227
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,780
Chief Zhang! Chief Zhang!

228
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,090
That video you just saw...

229
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,450
was from three days ago.

230
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,120
Why didn't you say so earlier?

231
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,980
You didn't ask.

232
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,120
Should we still pursue them?

233
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,850
Pursue what?

234
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,000
Never mind leaving the city—

235
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,530
they've probably left
the province already.

236
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,240
Chief,

237
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:33,390
we found the owner of the Land Rover!

238
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:38,060
The owner is Yang Wei,

239
00:11:37,650 --> 00:11:40,040
[Basic information; Name: Yang Wei]

240
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,410
an ex-convict

241
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:41,630
who's now living off loan sharking.

242
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,870
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau
Personal Information Form]

243
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:42,640
The car is his.

244
00:11:42,870 --> 00:11:43,390
Good.

245
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:44,980
Finding the owner

246
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,150
at least gives us something.

247
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,360
See if you can track down Yang Wei.

248
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,760
What did he go to jail for?

249
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,810
He got into a fight

250
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:52,910
defending his friend Lin Kai

251
00:11:52,910 --> 00:11:53,870
and left the other man

252
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:55,080
with a second-degree disability.

253
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,490
That's what got him sent in.

254
00:11:56,490 --> 00:11:58,220
[Gender: Male]

255
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:30,970
Is he at home?

256
00:12:32,310 --> 00:12:33,910
If he were, would I let you in?

257
00:12:35,610 --> 00:12:37,270
How many days has he been gone?

258
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,230
A few days.

259
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:42,240
Are you here for me,

260
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,030
or for him?

261
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:45,730
No, no.

262
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,080
Sister-in-law.

263
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,620
You're calling me "sister-in-law" now?

264
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,000
I really have something important.

265
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,930
Half an hour wouldn't hurt, right?

266
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,480
Are you coming in or not?

267
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:45,470
What are you doing?

268
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:46,670
Lin Kai isn't at home.

269
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:47,800
Where...

270
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:48,970
Where did he go?

271
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,080
How would I know?

272
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,490
Sister-in-law,

273
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:03,360
can you let me in to talk?

274
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,480
Oh, my.

275
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:05,510
A man and a woman alone—

276
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:07,170
how can you even suggest that?

277
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,120
Come out.

278
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:23,720
Looking for Lin Kai?

279
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,630
Can you stop bringing him up?

280
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:30,050
I haven't been able to reach him for days.

281
00:14:30,050 --> 00:14:32,780
I'm really worried
something's happened to him.

282
00:14:36,650 --> 00:14:37,630
If others see me like this,

283
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,490
it would be really embarrassing.

284
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:44,990
What could possibly happen to him?

285
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,030
He's probably off somewhere,

286
00:14:46,030 --> 00:14:47,830
fooling around with some woman.

287
00:14:52,110 --> 00:14:53,800
I have a bad feeling about this.

288
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,260
I need to find him quickly.

289
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,060
Are you still coming over?

290
00:14:58,630 --> 00:15:00,630
Don't be like this, Sister-in-law.

291
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:02,590
Kai and I are like real brothers.

292
00:15:04,310 --> 00:15:04,830
I know.

293
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:16,680
[Precise Phone Location]

294
00:15:18,390 --> 00:15:20,020
Isn't this illegal?

295
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,190
Obviously.

296
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,390
You can really track a phone?

297
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
What do you think?

298
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:32,660
Then help me track one.

299
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:37,610
Tell me your wife's phone number.

300
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,040
It's not my wife.

301
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:41,550
Just say your wife's number!

302
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:48,720
Excuse me.

303
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:04,650
Hello?

304
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:05,790
Is this Yang Wei?

305
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:06,200
Yes.

306
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:08,240
This is
the Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau.

307
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:10,300
We'd like to ask you about something.

308
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,670
The license plate's been changed

309
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:14,120
and the car's paint altered.

310
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,380
We've come back again.

311
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,540
Zhou Rong can still slip away from us?

312
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,200
Can he shake us?

313
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,970
He's a rat in a trap!

314
00:16:34,190 --> 00:16:36,190
Hold it in. Don't throw up in the car.

315
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:38,980
We're almost at the service area.

316
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:39,800
Hang in there.

317
00:16:42,650 --> 00:16:45,250
[Sandu Service Area]

318
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:53,870
Water.

319
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:00,210
-You okay?
-Water.

320
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,380
We're out of water.

321
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:05,380
Here, have a steamed bun
to settle your stomach.

322
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:10,000
Here.

323
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:13,440
Can't you at least buy me a bottle of...

324
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:17,550
What's wrong?

325
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:18,960
This isn't the one we bought for that jerk

326
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,920
that day, is it?

327
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,720
When did we buy it?

328
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:22,690
Yesterday.

329
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:24,790
Didn't give it to him?

330
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:25,480
I forgot.

331
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,920
So you haven't checked on him
these past few days,

332
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,780
and he hasn't made a sound either?

333
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,400
Whose phone is ringing?

334
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:14,400
His.

335
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,240
Find somewhere out of the way

336
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:21,970
and bury him.

337
00:18:29,470 --> 00:18:30,180
[Calling]

338
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:35,440
The line is busy.

339
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:37,040
The phone must be turned off.

340
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:39,010
Can you still track it then?

341
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,550
I'm a professional.

342
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:47,500
[September 6, 2012]

343
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,530
The owner of the Land Rover

344
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,200
is this guy, Yang Wei.

345
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:53,400
By comparing surveillance footage,
we've confirmed

346
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,200
the kidnapped person is Lin Kai.

347
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,090
They're very close—

348
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:58,410
sworn brothers.

349
00:18:58,680 --> 00:18:59,610
Sworn brothers?

350
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:00,790
And Liu Bei.

351
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,840
And there's another...

352
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,110
They also have a big brother
named Mei Dong,

353
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:06,160
who is also a wanted criminal

354
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,760
and has been fleeing abroad.

355
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:08,980
What a den of crooks.

356
00:19:09,070 --> 00:19:10,600
Quite the crew they've got.

357
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,560
As for

358
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,700
why Lin Kai was driving Yang Wei's car

359
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,160
and why the kidnappers took Lin Kai,

360
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:20,070
we can only get answers from Yang Wei.

361
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:20,930
Look at him.

362
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,840
He's clearly a regular here.

363
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:26,850
Doesn't look like the cooperative type.

364
00:19:27,750 --> 00:19:29,480
So, how should we question him?

365
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:41,480
Officers,

366
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,510
I really don't know anything.

367
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,710
It's no use asking me.

368
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,960
Lin Kai was kidnapped.

369
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,960
Did you know that?

370
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,480
That's still got nothing to do with me.

371
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,740
Nothing to do with you?

372
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:53,590
As far as we know,

373
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:55,960
there is a little conflict

374
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,240
between you

375
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,880
and your sworn brother.

376
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,060
What conflict?

377
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:41,800
Sit down.

378
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,810
Sworn brothers,

379
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,810
yet you could do such a thing to him.

380
00:20:48,510 --> 00:20:49,240
Did you think

381
00:20:49,270 --> 00:20:50,880
you were being careful enough

382
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:53,080
that you wouldn't get caught on camera?

383
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:54,350
Impossible. Well...

384
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:55,510
Is the video ready?

385
00:21:17,850 --> 00:21:19,580
Do you want us to play it for you?

386
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:27,240
Play it.

387
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:33,740
Are we really going to play it?

388
00:22:21,260 --> 00:22:21,740
Okay.

389
00:22:21,770 --> 00:22:22,790
Then let's

390
00:22:22,830 --> 00:22:23,890
enjoy it together.

391
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:26,320
I've slept with Ying.

392
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,320
State the relationship.

393
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,840
She's Lin Kai's wife.

394
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:35,770
Except for this, e-e-everything...

395
00:22:35,770 --> 00:22:37,480
everything between us
has been aboveboard. W-We...

396
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,240
We have no conflict.

397
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,300
"Except for this?"

398
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:40,840
Is that not a big deal?

399
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:41,880
Officer.

400
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,110
Lin Kai is away all year round. He...

401
00:22:45,110 --> 00:22:46,510
H-He just hires hookers.

402
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:47,310
For more than a year,

403
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,640
he barely touches Ying.

404
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,790
Well, Ying and I... I...

405
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:50,510
We are...

406
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:52,070
We are truly...

407
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,030
Sometimes we'd even...

408
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:55,410
cover his photo on the wall.

409
00:22:55,410 --> 00:22:56,940
He couldn't possibly know!

410
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:58,680
And i-it's even more impossible
for me to...

411
00:22:58,680 --> 00:23:00,080
W-Why would I kidnap him?

412
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,460
I'm innocent, officer!

413
00:23:01,460 --> 00:23:03,260
Whether you are innocent or not,

414
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,260
we will investigate thoroughly.

415
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:06,820
But first,

416
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:08,180
you need to cooperate.

417
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,170
I'll cooperate.

418
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,780
I definitely will.

419
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:17,160
[Subject: Yang Wei]

420
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:23,170
I-I-I can go now?

421
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:25,080
Don't leave the city for now.

422
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:26,840
Be available whenever we call.

423
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,000
I'm going now.

424
00:23:32,430 --> 00:23:33,110
Don't go yet.

425
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:34,040
Wait over there.

426
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,050
Stand outside and wait!

427
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:43,000
Customs just flagged someone—

428
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:44,060
possibly Mei Dong.

429
00:23:45,330 --> 00:23:46,790
Come on, Yang Wei. Come in.

430
00:23:47,770 --> 00:23:48,390
Come in.

431
00:23:49,410 --> 00:23:50,810
-You...
-You...

432
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:54,110
The affair
between you and your sister-in-law...

433
00:23:54,110 --> 00:23:55,440
Go home and sort that out.

434
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,570
Handle it properly.

435
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:58,310
Go.

436
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:06,250
Aren't you going to question him
about Mei Dong?

437
00:24:06,330 --> 00:24:07,010
Chief,

438
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:08,880
should we have Customs

439
00:24:08,900 --> 00:24:10,170
detain that person

440
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:11,720
and verify his identity?

441
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,310
No.

442
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,070
Just let him in.

443
00:24:15,350 --> 00:24:16,950
What if it really is Mei Dong?

444
00:24:17,350 --> 00:24:17,750
If he dares

445
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,030
to take such a huge risk to come back,

446
00:24:19,030 --> 00:24:19,720
he might be related

447
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:20,450
to this case.

448
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:22,400
Whether there's a big fish or not,

449
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,860
let's cast the line first.

450
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:25,580
Now it seems

451
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:26,720
Lin Kai and the kidnappers

452
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,240
only had a traffic dispute.

453
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:28,920
The kidnappers

454
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,110
wanted Lin Kai's car,

455
00:24:30,110 --> 00:24:31,370
so they kidnapped him.

456
00:24:33,330 --> 00:24:35,350
[Phone Location Results]
[Location: Sandu Expressway Service Area]

457
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,760
Why would he be

458
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:43,270
at the Sandu Expressway Service Area?

459
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,440
According to this,

460
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:46,840
he's at the Sandu Expressway Service Area.

461
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:47,480
[Phone Location Results]
[Location: Sandu Expressway Service Area]

462
00:24:50,030 --> 00:24:50,880
Thank you.

463
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:52,650
Well...

464
00:24:52,650 --> 00:24:53,400
Hold on!

465
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,680
Pay up!

466
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:56,180
How much?

467
00:24:57,500 --> 00:24:57,700
[Precise Phone Tracking: 200 per search]

468
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:10,150
Two thousand.

469
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,250
Money to burn.

470
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:18,410
[Precise Phone Tracking: 200 per search]

471
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,270
[Charge only after locating the target]

472
00:25:19,270 --> 00:25:19,950
[200]

473
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,480
Chao,

474
00:25:40,030 --> 00:25:41,760
I swear I didn't kill that jerk.

475
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:42,700
You even told me

476
00:25:42,700 --> 00:25:43,810
not to kill him.

477
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:45,690
Every time we stopped,

478
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,270
I even let him go to the bathroom

479
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,330
and gave him food.

480
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:50,120
I was very attentive to him.

481
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:50,880
I've never been

482
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,480
that attentive to my own dad.

483
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:53,180
Chao.

484
00:26:10,530 --> 00:26:12,660
The cuckold choked to death on his own.

485
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,300
So he choked to death.

486
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:17,020
Then it's not on us, right?

487
00:26:17,070 --> 00:26:18,070
You wish.

488
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:23,700
Come give me a hand.

489
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,690
He got carsick just like you.

490
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:37,110
But with a towel stuffed in his mouth,
he couldn't throw up.

491
00:26:37,110 --> 00:26:37,750
Everything in his stomach

492
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:39,280
surged up through his nose—

493
00:26:40,030 --> 00:26:40,960
he suffocated.

494
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:46,680
This death is on our hands,

495
00:26:46,680 --> 00:26:48,210
no matter how you look at it.

496
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:52,870
I was planning to

497
00:26:52,870 --> 00:26:54,600
let him go once the job was done.

498
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:57,400
After all, we've never
killed anyone before.

499
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,800
If we got caught someday,

500
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,630
the worst we'd done was robbery—

501
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:01,880
not a death sentence.

502
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,270
But once we have blood on our hands,

503
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,470
everything changes.

504
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,310
Then what do we do now?

505
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:20,680
Bury him.

506
00:27:22,220 --> 00:27:22,790
Where...

507
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,510
Where should we bury him?

508
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:27,220
This place may not be exactly scenic,

509
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,700
but it's spacious.

510
00:27:29,310 --> 00:27:31,110
Land prices being what they are,

511
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,350
and the location so convenient—

512
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,750
easy access to anywhere.

513
00:27:35,110 --> 00:27:36,440
We've done right by him.

514
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:58,040
Chao, aren't you going to help?

515
00:27:58,840 --> 00:27:59,770
I'll keep watch.

516
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:06,400
[Shengshun Taxi]

517
00:28:06,490 --> 00:28:07,360
Where to?

518
00:28:07,390 --> 00:28:08,860
Sandu Expressway Service Area, going?

519
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:10,000
No, it's too late!

520
00:28:08,890 --> 00:28:15,960
[Shengshun Taxi]

521
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:10,570
No!

522
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:11,880
It's not late, not late at all!

523
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:12,790
I'm not going that way.

524
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:13,590
I'm off shift!

525
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:14,350
It's too late.

526
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:15,480
It's not too late...

527
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:18,470
Driver,

528
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,910
Sandu Service Area, going?

529
00:28:19,910 --> 00:28:21,240
It's too far. Not going.

530
00:28:23,670 --> 00:28:31,060
[Vacant]

531
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:27,050
Why is no one hailing a cab?

532
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:28,890
You call this a cab?

533
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,930
It's literally like a tractor.

534
00:28:32,960 --> 00:28:40,200
[Vacant]

535
00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:33,840
That guy's hailing.

536
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:35,500
That guy's flagging one down.

537
00:28:43,070 --> 00:28:44,090
Sir, need a ride?

538
00:28:45,010 --> 00:28:45,940
Licensed taxi.

539
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:47,960
[Vacant]

540
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:48,110
Metered fare.

541
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:48,690
Right.

542
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:51,400
Out in the suburbs,
we always go two to a cab.

543
00:28:55,510 --> 00:28:56,480
You're still willing to

544
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,920
head to the suburbs this late?

545
00:28:57,920 --> 00:28:58,250
Yeah.

546
00:28:58,260 --> 00:28:59,260
Exactly. It's...

547
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:00,550
It's late, so there are two of us.

548
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,650
Safer this way.

549
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,850
Where are you going?

550
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:07,090
Sandu Service Area.

551
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:07,840
Perfect!

552
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,120
Perfect. Hop in.

553
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:09,640
I'm telling you,

554
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,200
you're lucky you ran into us.

555
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:11,960
Otherwise...

556
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:13,790
There aren't many cabs on this road.

557
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:14,680
You could be waiting till tomorrow morning

558
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,720
and still not get a ride.

559
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,660
Exactly.

560
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:17,480
Get in.

561
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:25,880
Okay.

562
00:29:26,030 --> 00:29:26,560
Let's go.

563
00:29:51,030 --> 00:29:51,590
You done?

564
00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:52,440
Yeah.

565
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,590
Where's the body?

566
00:30:03,710 --> 00:30:04,520
Right here.

567
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:17,480
You really treat him like your dad?

568
00:30:18,110 --> 00:30:19,480
Hey, I worked hard on this.

569
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,200
Don't just come here

570
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,360
and mock me.

571
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:22,550
No, I...

572
00:30:22,830 --> 00:30:24,030
I told you to dig a hole and bury him,

573
00:30:24,030 --> 00:30:25,200
but why did you build a grave

574
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,940
right in the middle of the road?

575
00:30:27,110 --> 00:30:28,590
Chao, you can't blame me for this.

576
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:29,640
I barely dug a few times,

577
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,440
and it was all rock underneath.

578
00:30:30,440 --> 00:30:31,480
I shoveled... Well...

579
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:32,960
How big was the rock?

580
00:30:34,330 --> 00:30:35,440
The entire city underground

581
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,270
is solid rock.

582
00:30:37,230 --> 00:30:37,920
Well...

583
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:41,160
Well, I just want to ask you—

584
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,160
since it's all rock down there,

585
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:43,820
where did this soil come from?

586
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,790
I dug a hole over there

587
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,030
and shoveled the soil over here

588
00:30:47,030 --> 00:30:47,610
one scoop at a time.

589
00:30:47,610 --> 00:30:48,940
I went back and forth...

590
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:51,400
You knew enough to dig a hole over there

591
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:53,720
and move the dirt here to bury the guy,

592
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:54,960
but it didn't occur to you

593
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,490
to just bury the body there?

594
00:31:00,840 --> 00:31:01,920
Dig the body up.

595
00:31:02,120 --> 00:31:02,890
Well, Chao!

596
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,680
I just made his grave,

597
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,420
and now y-you want to move it?

598
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:08,110
Well, Chao,

599
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:10,030
I can't bring myself to dig up graves!

600
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:10,940
Shut up!

601
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:13,290
I don't trust you anymore!

602
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:14,930
You go keep watch.

603
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:19,200
Well, Chao.

604
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,010
Let me do it!

605
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,240
Let me do it!

606
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:24,920
Chao, let me do it!

607
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,450
Get lost!

608
00:31:50,190 --> 00:31:50,780
Chao,

609
00:31:51,180 --> 00:31:52,580
you really are the pro here.

610
00:31:52,580 --> 00:31:54,150
It can fit another body.

611
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:56,000
Why don't you lie in there then?

612
00:31:57,270 --> 00:31:57,880
Bury him.

613
00:32:00,710 --> 00:32:02,110
You won't move the grave,

614
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:04,850
but you can't even fill the pit properly?

615
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:30,610
Is this okay?

616
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:31,470
Let's go.

617
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:32,310
Wait a minute.

618
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:42,550
[Cables Below; Do Not Dig]

619
00:32:48,090 --> 00:32:51,680
[Cables Below; Do Not Dig]

620
00:32:52,150 --> 00:32:53,080
Is it okay, Chao?

621
00:32:53,310 --> 00:32:53,920
Classic

622
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:56,490
"no silver buried here," huh?
Really subtle.

623
00:32:56,720 --> 00:32:57,920
I'll put it back then.

624
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:00,060
It's fine.

625
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,350
Let's just leave it at that.

626
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,680
Where are we going next?

627
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:03,650
Back to the city.

628
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:06,140
We need to hurry up with this job.

629
00:33:41,050 --> 00:33:41,700
In a bit,

630
00:33:42,410 --> 00:33:43,470
I'll pull over.

631
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,720
You grab the hammer

632
00:33:46,270 --> 00:33:48,110
and go to the back
to get the money from that dude.

633
00:33:48,110 --> 00:33:50,370
If he won't hand it over,
cave his head in.

634
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:52,230
Why don't you go?

635
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:53,880
I'm driving, aren't I?

636
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:56,570
You started this mess.

637
00:33:56,570 --> 00:33:57,160
You go.

638
00:34:02,130 --> 00:34:03,400
It's just killing someone.

639
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,010
You do it.

640
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:05,110
You got it.

641
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:07,240
"Just killing someone?"

642
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:07,920
You make it sound

643
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,190
like buying groceries.

644
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:09,790
You go.

645
00:34:10,110 --> 00:34:11,650
Tinggang, you go.

646
00:34:11,670 --> 00:34:12,360
You go.

647
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,620
You take it.

648
00:34:13,650 --> 00:34:14,860
You go. You...

649
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:19,760
I just...

650
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:20,110
Crap...

651
00:34:20,110 --> 00:34:20,770
He ran away.

652
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,710
My fault now?

653
00:34:39,230 --> 00:34:40,760
I didn't even say anything.

654
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:43,010
You were saying it in your head.

655
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,780
I wasn't even thinking it.

656
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:48,940
Well then, d-d-do

657
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:49,820
we chase him?

658
00:34:50,050 --> 00:34:51,580
Chase what? We're exposed.

659
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:52,600
Let's go.

660
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:04,740
[Cables Below; Do Not Dig]

661
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,060
Take the body away.

662
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:38,950
-Chen.
-Chen.

663
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,640
Chief, Captain Wang.

664
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:42,900
Who reported this?

665
00:35:43,070 --> 00:35:44,470
It was an anonymous call.

666
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,390
We traced it.

667
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,000
It was from a public phone booth.

668
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:48,000
An anonymous tip?

669
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,920
Have we verified the victim's identity?

670
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,030
The victim is Lin Kai.

671
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:51,710
Time of death

672
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:53,050
was over 48 hours ago.

673
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:55,360
So did the kidnappers

674
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:56,420
kill him

675
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,480
before leaving Sanjiangkou,

676
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:59,140
or did they come back and do it?

677
00:35:59,320 --> 00:36:00,580
We've been monitoring

678
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,180
all the highway exits.

679
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,860
No sign of them returning.

680
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:04,960
Let's wait for Chen's

681
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,800
autopsy results.

682
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:06,860
If the time of death

683
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,140
is over 72 hours ago,

684
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,070
it means

685
00:36:09,110 --> 00:36:10,770
they killed him before leaving.

686
00:36:10,770 --> 00:36:11,590
If the time of death

687
00:36:11,590 --> 00:36:12,930
is within 72 hours,

688
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,030
they must have come back

689
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:15,080
and likely switched vehicles.

690
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:22,710
[Police]

691
00:36:16,630 --> 00:36:17,030
Chief.

692
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,160
Captain Wang.

693
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,150
We can basically rule out

694
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,280
robbery as a motive.

695
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:22,310
The phone and wallet are both on the body,

696
00:36:22,310 --> 00:36:24,770
and there's still a lot of cash
in the wallet.

697
00:36:25,770 --> 00:36:27,380
[Jinshuiting]

698
00:36:30,130 --> 00:36:31,190
What does this say?

699
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:37,570
[Jinshuiting]

700
00:36:33,860 --> 00:36:35,400
This is the suspect's backpack.

701
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:36,920
There are only a few clothes inside.

702
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,320
It's written in cursive.

703
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:39,590
Hegegao.

704
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:40,560
Jinshuiting.

705
00:36:40,580 --> 00:36:42,710
It should be pronounced Jinshuiting.

706
00:36:43,130 --> 00:36:44,660
[Jinshuiting]

707
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,230
Hegegao.

708
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:53,950
[Police]

709
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:51,440
Hegegao.

710
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:52,220
What?

711
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:54,130
It's "Jinshuiting."

712
00:36:55,950 --> 00:36:58,410
Same as the character
on Liu Bei's backpack.

713
00:37:00,570 --> 00:37:01,500
Summon Yang Wei.

714
00:37:03,390 --> 00:37:06,950
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau
Personal Information Form]

715
00:37:12,070 --> 00:37:13,670
Li Feng has confessed it all.

716
00:37:14,090 --> 00:37:15,890
He is a Class-A wanted criminal.

717
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:16,710
This time,

718
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:18,280
you finally caught him.

719
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,740
Lin Kai is really gone?

720
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,290
Can you still hold it together?

721
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,760
We called you in today

722
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:17,310
to talk about Jinshuiting.

723
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:20,170
How much do you know

724
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,290
about this gang?

725
00:38:24,190 --> 00:38:25,300
Jinshuiting...

726
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:27,150
was, you could say,

727
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:28,350
our first pot of gold.

728
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,390
At that time, our big brother,

729
00:38:30,390 --> 00:38:32,190
Mei Dong, handled the channels.

730
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:34,160
Liu Bei managed the supply.

731
00:38:36,030 --> 00:38:37,760
Well, Liu Bei robbed the tombs,

732
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:39,660
and Dong fenced the stolen items.

733
00:38:40,030 --> 00:38:41,040
Lin Kai and I

734
00:38:41,070 --> 00:38:42,600
handled market expansion.

735
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:44,600
Later on,

736
00:38:44,630 --> 00:38:46,030
the business got better.

737
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,630
We all had money.

738
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:49,920
The first time I ever had abalone

739
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:50,900
was at that...

740
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:55,220
The company was started by Mei Dong?

741
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:58,700
And after that?

742
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:02,570
And after that,

743
00:39:02,630 --> 00:39:03,440
Jinshuiting's business

744
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,500
just kept growing.

745
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,250
Then...

746
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:07,880
D-Dong and Liu Bei started thinking about

747
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,610
how to take the business

748
00:39:08,610 --> 00:39:09,610
to the next level.

749
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:11,760
Then they decided to

750
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,310
crowdfund—

751
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:15,320
to rob
the Mausoleum of the First Qin Emperor.

752
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,120
I heard.

753
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,770
You guys really dared to dream big.

754
00:39:18,770 --> 00:39:19,510
If you were in Egypt,

755
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:21,110
would you have gone to
dig up the pyramids?

756
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,170
We surveyed it.

757
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:24,410
The pyramids in Egypt,

758
00:39:24,670 --> 00:39:26,150
the ancient city of Pompeii in Italy,

759
00:39:26,150 --> 00:39:28,080
and the Mayan temples in Honduras—

760
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,740
Dong checked them all out.

761
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,110
That's why they say

762
00:39:31,110 --> 00:39:32,880
you need to get out and see the world.

763
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:33,840
The more places you see,

764
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:36,000
the more you realize
how good things are back home.

765
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:36,800
Those places—

766
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:38,550
t-there's nothing left underground.

767
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:39,550
It's still our country
that has the good stuff.

768
00:39:39,550 --> 00:39:42,110
-So much treasure is buried...
-Stick to the point.

769
00:39:42,110 --> 00:39:42,930
And then what?

770
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:46,400
And then... Well...

771
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,840
The crowdfunded tomb-robbing scheme

772
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:49,770
got discovered.

773
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,960
The two of them killed someone over it

774
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:54,820
and e-ended up on the wanted list.

775
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:57,490
So Dong fled to Southeast Asia.

776
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:58,760
That's when we

777
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,960
went our separate ways.

778
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,160
Mei Dong has a murder charge on him, huh?

779
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,970
So what was he doing in Southeast Asia?

780
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,610
Started a new business.

781
00:40:08,230 --> 00:40:09,490
What kind of business?

782
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,840
Financial derivatives.

783
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:16,460
Just l-loan sharking.

784
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:19,710
He provided capital from overseas,

785
00:40:20,110 --> 00:40:21,550
while Lin Kai and I handled

786
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:23,030
debt collection and lending here.

787
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:24,160
Just loan sharking?

788
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:26,280
A-And money laundering.

789
00:40:29,460 --> 00:40:30,660
Tell us about Liu Bei.

790
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:34,720
I-I really don't know about him.

791
00:40:35,510 --> 00:40:36,630
We haven't been in touch for a long time.

792
00:40:36,630 --> 00:40:38,320
I-I just heard that he...

793
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:40,320
he might still be doing his old trade.

794
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:41,750
Besides tomb raiding,

795
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,070
has Liu Bei been

796
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:45,170
negotiating some big deal recently?

797
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:46,970
About...

798
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:48,250
some big artifact?

799
00:40:50,550 --> 00:40:51,220
Well...

800
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,860
I really... really...

801
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:54,940
really don't know.

802
00:40:56,630 --> 00:40:58,090
Mei Dong is back, you know?

803
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:02,060
Impossible.

804
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,920
Absolutely impossible.

805
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,470
He's a wanted criminal.

806
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:07,190
He wouldn't dare come back
even if his own mother died.

807
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:08,790
Doesn't he value your bonds?

808
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,890
Your good buddy Lin Kai died.

809
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:12,800
Wouldn't he come back for that?

810
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:14,930
He is a loyal friend.

811
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:18,310
There's real brotherhood between us.

812
00:41:19,630 --> 00:41:20,560
I'm telling you,

813
00:41:21,020 --> 00:41:22,080
Mei Dong is back.

814
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:25,440
Help me get him to come out.

815
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:27,100
That's impossible.

816
00:41:27,670 --> 00:41:28,360
No, officer.

817
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,230
I-It's not that I don't want to help you.

818
00:41:30,230 --> 00:41:32,290
H-He really wouldn't dare come back.

819
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:32,960
He...

820
00:41:35,870 --> 00:41:36,580
[Dong]

821
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:38,650
It's M-Mei Dong.

822
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:42,990
[Dong]

823
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,730
You know what to say, eh?

824
00:41:50,810 --> 00:41:51,930
Don't stutter.

825
00:41:54,500 --> 00:41:57,870
[Dong]

826
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:00,680
D-Dong.

827
00:42:00,710 --> 00:42:01,420
Wei,

828
00:42:01,670 --> 00:42:03,070
I'm back in Sanjiangkou.

829
00:42:03,190 --> 00:42:04,590
Do you have time tonight?

830
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:06,900
I-I do.

831
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,560
Why did you come back?

832
00:42:10,550 --> 00:42:11,320
W-W-Why did you

833
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,840
come back so suddenly?

834
00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:15,070
There's a big deal in Sanjiangkou.

835
00:42:15,070 --> 00:42:16,880
I came back to negotiate personally.

836
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:17,710
If it goes through,

837
00:42:17,710 --> 00:42:20,170
we won't need to work
for three to five years.

838
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:22,050
Then let's say 7 PM,

839
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:23,440
in the Guanlan Hotel lobby.

840
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,440
I'll wait for you.

841
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:26,360
You...

842
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:28,480
Didn't you say

843
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:31,010
he wouldn't come back
even if his mother died?

844
00:42:32,190 --> 00:42:34,120
You haven't been straight with us.

845
00:42:35,140 --> 00:42:37,340
[Investigation Area]

846
00:42:40,600 --> 00:42:49,200
[Investigation Area]

847
00:42:46,150 --> 00:42:46,630
Chief,

848
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:48,760
what does catching Mei Dong
have to do with

849
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:50,590
us investigating Zhou Rong and his men?

850
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:52,120
It has nothing to do with it.

851
00:42:52,230 --> 00:42:52,920
If it doesn't,

852
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,520
why are we catching Mei Dong?

853
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:57,530
Mei Dong has a big deal to negotiate.

854
00:42:57,820 --> 00:42:59,110
Liu Bei has a big business to conduct.

855
00:42:59,110 --> 00:43:00,910
And they both end up in this city.

856
00:43:01,110 --> 00:43:02,420
I have a feeling there's something bigger

857
00:43:02,420 --> 00:43:03,450
going on here.

858
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:05,050
Chief Zhang.

859
00:43:06,110 --> 00:43:07,110
Lin Kai's time of death

860
00:43:07,110 --> 00:43:08,510
was within the last 72 hours.

861
00:43:08,510 --> 00:43:09,510
It must have been those two kidnappers

862
00:43:09,510 --> 00:43:10,230
returning.

863
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:11,670
Report it to Director Gao.

864
00:43:11,670 --> 00:43:13,150
It should satisfy him, right?

865
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:14,770
I-I also have some news.

866
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:15,880
Mei Dong called.

867
00:43:16,880 --> 00:43:17,400
He's arranged to meet Yang Wei

868
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:18,370
tonight at 7 PM

869
00:43:18,510 --> 00:43:19,820
at the Guanlan Hotel.

870
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,330
It really was him.

871
00:43:22,000 --> 00:43:22,710
What is he doing back here?

872
00:43:22,710 --> 00:43:23,550
Trying to get himself caught?

873
00:43:23,550 --> 00:43:26,030
Mei Dong said he came back
to negotiate a deal.

874
00:43:26,030 --> 00:43:26,920
After all his years

875
00:43:26,920 --> 00:43:28,840
laundering money in Southeast Asia,

876
00:43:28,840 --> 00:43:30,560
for him to show up in person,

877
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:32,360
the amount must be enormous.

878
00:43:33,230 --> 00:43:34,710
They think they can come and go

879
00:43:34,710 --> 00:43:35,630
whenever they want?

880
00:43:35,630 --> 00:43:36,360
Not a chance.

881
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:37,810
In their dreams.

882
00:43:37,880 --> 00:43:38,510
Then, let's move quickly

883
00:43:38,510 --> 00:43:39,590
and arrange an arrest.

884
00:43:39,590 --> 00:43:39,960
Okay.

885
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:46,570
Sit out the operation tonight.

886
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:48,510
I have an even more important task

887
00:43:48,510 --> 00:43:49,210
for you.

888
00:43:50,030 --> 00:43:51,370
Organize the materials

889
00:43:51,440 --> 00:43:53,030
for the provincial task force first,

890
00:43:53,030 --> 00:43:54,530
and send them to Director Gao.

891
00:43:54,530 --> 00:43:55,280
There's one thing

892
00:43:55,280 --> 00:43:56,590
that needs to be made absolutely clear:

893
00:43:56,590 --> 00:43:58,590
request that jurisdiction
be formally assigned to us

894
00:43:58,590 --> 00:44:00,450
so we can lead the investigation.

895
00:44:00,800 --> 00:44:01,530
We will report

896
00:44:01,530 --> 00:44:02,670
all developments in real time

897
00:44:02,670 --> 00:44:05,230
and hand over the suspects
according to regulations afterward.

898
00:44:05,230 --> 00:44:06,430
Be clear about it,

899
00:44:06,670 --> 00:44:08,190
but keep the wording tactful.

900
00:44:08,190 --> 00:44:09,800
After all, they're from
the Provincial Department.

901
00:44:09,800 --> 00:44:11,320
Organizing materials again?

902
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,690
I'm fully recovered.

903
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:14,550
I know you're fully recovered.

904
00:44:14,550 --> 00:44:16,350
But can I trust others to do this?

905
00:44:16,710 --> 00:44:17,440
Wang Ruijun?

906
00:44:17,550 --> 00:44:18,150
Song Xing?

907
00:44:21,840 --> 00:44:22,760
Understood. Consider it done.
